<h3 id="add">Add</h3>
    <p>There are several ways for adding the block in qoob. </p>
     <ol>
     	<li>To add a block in the page, please, <code>click</code> on the block.</li> 
         <p><img src="img/press.png"></p>
          <p>Each new block is added to the end of the page, under the blocks that were added earlier. After that you can add blocks by <code>dragging</code>. </p>
         <li>You find a block in the group and <code>move</code> it to the necessary place. This place will be highlighted as it is shown here.</li>
            <p><img src="img/drag.png"></p>
            </ol>
 <h3 id="edit">Edit</h3>
        <p>You can edit information in each block of the page. For this purpose<code> click</code> the necessary block on the right of the page. In the left you can see settings of this block.</p>
        <p><img src="img/edit.png"></p>
